<lb n="0364b06"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"></milestone>
<lb n="0364b07"/>
<lb n="0364b08"/><head type="no">No. 373</head>
<lb n="0364b09"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="1" type="卷"></mulu>後出阿彌陀佛<note n="0364002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">偈＋（經）【三】＊</note><note n="0364002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">偈＋（經）【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0364002"><lem>偈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">偈經</rdg></app></juan>
<lb n="0364b10"/>
<lb n="0364b11"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0364003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（古舊…錄））十三字＝（（後漢失譯））【宋】，（（後漢失譯師名））【元】【明】</note><app n="0364003" word-count="13"><lem>古舊錄云闕譯人名今紀後漢錄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">後漢失譯</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">後漢失譯師名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0364b12"/><div1 type="jing"><lg><l>惟念法比丘</l><l>乃從世饒王</l>
<lb n="0364b13"/><l>發願喻諸佛</l><l>誓二十四章</l>
<lb n="0364b14"/><l>世世見諸佛</l><l><note n="0364004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00108;＝垓【宋】</note><app n="0364004"><lem>&CB00108;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">垓</rdg></app>數無有量</l>
<lb n="0364b15"/><l>不廢宿命行</l><l>功德遂具成</l>
<lb n="0364b16"/><l>世界名清淨</l><l>得佛號無量</l>
<lb n="0364b17"/><l>國界平夷易</l><l>豐樂多上人</l>
<lb n="0364b18"/><l>寶樹若干種</l><l>羅列叢相生</l>
<lb n="0364b19"/><l>本莖枝葉花</l><l>種種各異香</l>
<lb n="0364b20"/><l>順風日三動</l><l>翕習如花生</l>
<lb n="0364b21"/><l>墮地如手布</l><l>雜廁上普平</l>
<lb n="0364b22"/><l>一切無諸山</l><l>海水及諸源</l>
<lb n="0364b23"/><l>但有河水流</l><l>音響如說經</l>
<lb n="0364b24"/><l>天人入水戲</l><l>在意所欲望</l>
<lb n="0364b25"/><l>令水齊胳肩</l><l>意願隨念得</l>
<lb n="0364b26"/><l>佛壽十方沙</l><l>光明普無邊</l>
<lb n="0364b27"/><l>菩薩及弟子</l><l>不可算稱量</l>
<lb n="0364b28"/><l>若欲見彼佛</l><l>莫疑亦莫<note n="0364005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忘＝望【三】</note><note n="0364005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忘＝望【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0364005"><lem>忘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">望</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0364b29"/><l>有疑在胎中</l><l>不合五百年</l>
<pb n="0364c" id="T12.0373.0364c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0364c01"/><l>不疑生<note n="0364006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">基＝臺【元】【明】</note><app n="0364006"><lem>基</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">臺</rdg></app>坐</l><l>叉手無量前</l>
<lb n="0364c02"/><l>願欲遍十方</l><l>須臾則旋還</l>
<lb n="0364c03"/><l>惟念彼菩薩</l><l>&CB00108;劫作功勤</l>
<lb n="0364c04"/><l>本行如此致</l><l>得號<app><lem>會</lem><rdg wit="【大】">憎</rdg></app>世尊</l>
<lb n="0364c05"/><l>佛興難得值</l><l>須臾會難聞</l>
<lb n="0364c06"/><l>講說<note n="0364007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">士＝大【宋】【元】</note><app n="0364007"><lem>士</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>難遇</l><l>受學人難得</l>
<lb n="0364c07"/><l>若後遭末世</l><l>法欲衰微時</l>
<lb n="0364c08"/><l>當共建擁護</l><l>行佛無欲法</l>
<lb n="0364c09"/><l>佛能說此要</l><l><note n="0364008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各各＝各當【三】</note><note n="0364008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各各＝各當【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0364008"><lem>各各</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">各當</rdg></app>勤思行</l>
<lb n="0364c10"/><l><note n="0364009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝弘【三】</note><note n="0364009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝弘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0364009"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">弘</rdg></app>此無量<note n="0364010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＝誓【三】</note><note n="0364010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">福＝誓【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0364010"><lem>福</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">誓</rdg></app></l><l>世世稽首行</l></lg>
<lb n="0364c11"/><juan n="001" fun="close">後出阿彌陀佛<app type="＊" source="0364002"><lem>偈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">偈經</rdg></app></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>